OL,3,CKhamenei's death leaves Iran's Islamic
OL,4,CRepublic facing its greatest test
OL,6,FHis life was dominated by the doctrine
OL,7,Fof the Islamic Revolution and driven
OL,8,Fby a belief in death to America and
OL,9,Fdeath to Israel.
OL,11,FThe death of Iran's Supreme Leader has
OL,12,Fcome through the acts of his two great
OL,13,Ffoes. A joint military attack on the
OL,14,Fcountry he ruled and the regime he led
OL,15,Fsince 1989.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
