OL,3,CKhamenei's death leaves Iran's Islamic
OL,4,CRepublic facing its greatest test
OL,6,FAt 86, who comes next has been a
OL,7,Fsubject of intense speculation inside
OL,8,FIran and beyond. During the 12-day war
OL,9,Fin June last year, a three-candidate
OL,10,Fsuccession plan was drawn up to ensure
OL,11,Fa smooth transition. It looks likely
OL,12,Fthat may now have to come into play.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772467873
OL,3,CKhamenei's death leaves Iran's Islamic
OL,4,CRepublic facing its greatest test
OL,6,FHowever, that was before the protests
OL,7,Fof the past months and before the
OL,8,Fdirect attempt by the US and Israel at
OL,9,Fregime change. Iran's clerical
OL,10,Fleadership is at its weakest point in
OL,11,Fits near half-century of rule.
OL,12,FHowever, without a massive social
OL,13,Fshift, the death of the leader does
OL,14,Fnot necessarily hasten the death of
OL,15,Fthe authoritarian governance he built.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
