OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772467873
OL,3,CKhamenei's death leaves Iran's Islamic
OL,4,CRepublic facing its greatest test
OL,6,FFor a managed transition, as
OL,7,Fdetermined by the doctrines of the
OL,8,Frepublic, his successor would need to
OL,9,Fbe approved by the Assembly of
OL,10,FExperts. They will be seeking a swift
OL,11,Fand smooth transition as a show of
OL,12,Fstrength.
OL,14,FHowever it may be this is the moment
OL,15,Fthe IRGC, the feared Revolutionary
OL,16,FGuard, so strengthened by Khamenei,
OL,17,Fdecide to take their chance and seek
OL,18,Fmilitary governance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
