OL,3,CKhamenei's death leaves Iran's Islamic
OL,4,CRepublic facing its greatest test
OL,6,FThe third, but most unlikely option,
OL,7,Fis that given the desperate state of
OL,8,Fthe country now, there is a move
OL,9,Ftowards a more reformist leadership.
OL,11,FPresident Trump is urging the Iranian
OL,12,Fpeople to seize their moment but the
OL,13,Fpopulation is not a monolith and
OL,14,Fthough many will cheer his demise, a
OL,15,Fsignificant proportion will not.
OL,16,FFurthermore, he was and remains one of
OL,17,Fthe most revered figures of Shia
OL,18,FIslam. It is unlikely his death will
OL,19,Fgo unmarked by retaliation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
